<FONT FACE="Courier New">

<H2><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C"><B>           COME, O SPIRIT CREATOR</B></FONT></H2>
<H2><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C"><B>HYMN OF VESPERS FROM ASCENSION TO PENTECOST</B></FONT></H2>
<H3><PRE>

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">    Am                G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A.  Come, O creator Spirit,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">               Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    visit our minds,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                    G
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    fill with your love 
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">                          Am
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    the hearts you have created.
                                 
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C.  O sweet Consoler,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    gift of the most high Father,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    living water, fire, love,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    holy chrism of the soul.
                                 
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A.  Finger of the hand of God,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    promised by the Saviour,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    pour out your seven gifts,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    make the word be born in us.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C.  Be light to the intellect,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    living flame in our hearts;
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    heal our wounds 
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    with the balm of your love.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A.  Defend us from the enemy,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    bring peace as your gift;
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    may your unfailing guidance
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    save us from all evil.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">C.  Light of eternal wisdom,
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    reveal to us the great mystery
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    of God the Father and the Son
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">    united in one single Love.

</FONT><FONT COLOR="#A13F3C">    G Am                              
</FONT><FONT COLOR="#000000">A.  Amen.
</PRE></H3>
</BODY>
</HTML>
